00002000 = Right (Left Analog)
00004000 = UP (Right ANALOG)
00008000 = Down (Right ANALOG)
00010000 = LEFT (Right Analog)
00020000 = Right (Right Analog)
00040000 = X
00080000 = Circle
00100000 = Triangle
