[Shadow Dancer Codes\Dog Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=If the dog is always set to follow you, it will even appear during boss battles, but won't be able to attack bosses. Not having the dog with you adds a degree of difficulty to the game.
Values -
00 - Dog always follows you
01 - Dog is never around
patch=1,EE,004716A6,extended,00000000

